once.  Notice I said nothing about FINISHING it.  As for Mishima, I've got one of 
his books -- although where it is and what it's called both escape me at the 
moment -- but I haven't read it yet.  I've got a book called The Master of Go

Mishima's although what I've read says the two could not have been more dissimilar in 
their personalities.  I have started it, but never finished it.  One of those 
books where one says "Huh?" and not in a good way, although I may give it 
another try and I suppose my attitude will change about it, but I wouldn't count 
on it.
